textBeforeTable: a few new screenshots. BioShock Infinite shows off more of the first-person shooter sequel in development at Irrational Games. The "City in the Sky" video includes gameplay footage showing off the serenity of the floating city of Columbia which is interrupted by the game's story, resulting in bullets, explosions, and the inexorable pull of gravity. The clip is accompanied by new trailer from A [Jan 31, 2013, 10:37 am ET] - Share - Viewing Comments BioShock Infinite 'City in the Sky' Trailer --> Blue's News Favorite! Join Blue's News!
